<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span> صحيح ـ <span class="c2">((غاية المرام)</span>) <span class="c2">(٥٧)</span>، <span class="c2">((الروض)</span>) <span class="c2">(٨٥٦)</span>: م.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ أَبُو حَاتِمٍ:</span> غَرِيبٌ غَرِيبٌ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>